   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# ErrP Personalization — Fully Upgraded Pipeline v2.0\n",
    "\n",
    "**Dataset**: INRIA BCI Challenge NER 2015 (26 subjects, LOSO evaluation)\n",
    "**Goal**: Few-shot personalization of Error-Related Potential (ErrP) detection\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "### Summary of all fixes in this version\n",
    "\n",
    "**Preprocessing (all critical)**\n",
    "- Bandpass 1–40 Hz + notch 50 Hz applied to *continuous* EEG before epoching  \n",
    "- Artifact rejection on raw µV (peak-to-peak > 100 µV) before normalization  \n",
    "- Per-epoch per-channel baseline correction (−200 ms to 0 ms)  \n",
    "- Epoch–label alignment by feedback index, not positional truncation\n",
    "\n",
    "**Architecture**\n",
    "- Encoder: 3-layer MLP with LayerNorm + GELU + no final activation (256→128→64)\n",
    "- SubjectEncoder: label-aware prototype encoder (error/correct/diff prototypes)\n",
    "- FiLM: LayerNorm before modulation; embed_dim=32 consistent everywhere\n",
    "- MAML/ANIL: CosineAnnealingLR, gradient clipping, class-weighted loss, balanced episodes\n",
    "- Reptile: corrected outer update (direct weight interpolation — no optimizer)\n",
    "- ProtoNets: cross-subject episodes, augmentation at K<10\n",
    "- Matching Networks: learnable softmax temperature\n",
    "- EEGNet: kernel_length=sfreq//2; closed-form LogisticRegression linear probe\n",
    "- Riemannian: xDAWN(n_filters=4) spatial filtering before covariance\n",
    "\n",
    "**Evaluation**\n",
    "- Primary metrics: balanced accuracy + AUC-ROC (not raw accuracy)\n",
    "- N_SEEDS=3 (was 1), K_SHOTS=[5,10,20] (K=50 removed — not few-shot)\n",
    "- Zero-shot baseline added; chance level (50%) made explicit\n",
    "- Effect sizes (rank-biserial r) alongside every p-value\n",
    "- Per-fold GPU memory cleanup + checkpoint saving\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
